      "writtenOn": "2026-06-23T12:28:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Now that n_bytes is u64, this comparator should not subtract and return the result as int. Large differences can truncate or compare equal when returned to qsort, which can misorder the trace list and hide the largest sites from the non-verbose top-50 output. Please switch to explicit comparisons for n_bytes, and do the same for n_allocations if it is widened to u64.",
      "revId": "f94f488c31a52bc1133560409fa3bcd707f2ae12",
      "serverId": "6d2eb258-4fe2-443e-8a38-ca81da23d4c2"
    },
    {
